und floor offers complete comfort, while the two secondary bedrooms on the ground floor, which share a full bathroom, also ensure practical and accessible living."}],"\n",["$","p","p-1",{"children":"The property features a kitchen completely remodeled in 2025, equipped with stainless steel appliances. The kitchen design is spacious and bright, integrating through a door with the dining room and family room, creating an ideal space for family gatherings and entertainment. The laundry area is enormous and includes a service room with a bathroom and independent access from the side of the house."}],"\n",["$","p","p-2",{"children":"The family room, spacious and filled with natural light, is perfect for spending time with family or enjoying an entertainment space. The finishes are high-quality, with guachipelín wood floors in the social areas, lending a warm and elegant touch. The formal living room has direct access to the large covered terrace with a garden."}],"\n",["$","p","p-3",{"children":"The property offers a total of 5 bedrooms distributed in a practical design. On the ground floor, in addition to the main bedroom, there are two secondary bedrooms that share a remodeled full bathroom. On the second floor, there is a full bathroom in the hallway and two additional secondary bedrooms, perfect for accommodating the entire family. Additionally, there is a half bathroom for guests."}],"\n",["$","p","p-4",{"children":"Key Property Features:"}],"\n",["$","p","p-5",{"children":"Lot: 762 m²\nConstruction: 477 m²\nBedrooms: 5 (including the ground-floor master bedroom and 2 ground-floor secondary bedrooms)\nBathrooms: 3.5 (includes a shared full bathroom on the ground floor and an additional full bathroom on the second floor)\nRemodeled kitchen\nFamily room and TV room\nSpacious terrace with garden access\nEnormous laundry area\n24/7 Security"}]]}]]}],null,["$","section",null,{"className":"border-t border-border pt-8","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"font-serif te